        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          What's the best POS system for a pet store?
          <span class="faq-icon"><i class="ti ti-plus"></i></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>It depends on your scale. For independent pet stores with heavy grooming and daycare scheduling, pet-specific platforms like Gingr, PetStack, or SuperPet Cloud are strong choices. For multi-location pet retail chains (10+ stores) that need enterprise inventory management, centralized fleet control, integrated omnichannel (BOPIS, ship-from-store, subscriptions), loyalty programs, and the Shopper Services POS advertising platform, Teamwork Commerce is the enterprise-grade option — proven at scale with Petco Mexico's 118-store, 2,000+ terminal deployment.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          Can Teamwork Commerce handle retail, grooming, and veterinary on one system?
          <span class="faq-icon"><i class="ti ti-plus"></i></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. Teamwork's multi-app iOS platform runs POS Pro (retail transactions), Drawer Memo (cash management), and Scheduler (grooming and vet appointments) on the same device. Royal Pets manages retail sales, veterinary appointments, and grooming on one platform. One training process, one customer view, one reporting suite.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          How does Teamwork Commerce compare to pet-specific POS like Gingr, PetStack, or SuperPet Cloud?
          <span class="faq-icon"><i class="ti ti-plus"></i></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Pet-specific platforms like Gingr and PetStack are excellent for independent pet stores with heavy grooming and daycare scheduling needs. Teamwork Commerce is built for multi-location pet retail chains that need enterprise infrastructure: centralized management of 100+ stores, real-time inventory across the fleet, integrated OMS for click-and-collect and ship-from-store, loyalty with targeted POS advertising (Shopper Services), and global compliance. Petco Mexico's 118-store, 2,000+ terminal deployment is proof of that scale.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          What is Shopper Services?
          <span class="faq-icon"><i class="ti ti-plus"></i></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Shopper Services is a revenue stream built into the POS. It serves targeted video ads and brand-sponsored promotions on customer-facing displays during checkout, personalized to each customer's pet profile and purchase history. Pet brands pay premium prices to reach the right pet owner at the exact moment of purchase. Retailers control ad values and targeting criteria.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          How did Petco Mexico deploy across 118 stores?
